data.description: Priced well below market value which means instant equity! USDA ($0 DOWN) approved - ask your local mortgage lender for more information! Welcome to this pristine 3-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Purcell, Oklahoma. Situated on a spacious half-acre lot with serene greenbelt views, this property offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and natural beauty. As you step inside you are greeted with great natural light and several updates throughout the home. Large living room open concept dining room is perfect for entertaining or quality time with the family. Whether you're preparing daily meals or hosting special occasions, this kitchen is sure to inspire your inner chef with double ovens and an abundant amount of countertop space. Cozy up by the wood burning fireplace in your second living room area. Each bedroom provides a cozy retreat, and the master suite boasts its own private en-suite bathroom for added convenience. Additional features include 2 car attached garage, large laundry/mud room, partial basement storage, public utilities. Plumbing has been recently replaced from the house and all down the street. Convenient location close to local amenities, schools, and parks. Don't miss your opportunity to make this remarkable property your own.
